<h1>Mongoid UTC Times</h1>
<p>By default Mongoid will store your Time objects in your local timezone.
It&#39;s not made clear on the <a href="http://mongoid.org/docs/installation/">installation
page</a>, but all you have to do is
add &quot;use_utc: true&quot; to the defaults in your mongoid.yml configuration
file. Yes Virginia, it&#39;s that simple.</p>
